title: HOUR 3: Eric Pincus and Confidence Rankings!
itunes:title: HOUR 3: Eric Pincus and Confidence Rankings!
description:
Jason Smith and Rob Parker rank their confidence in the top-seeded teams in the NBA postseason and speak with Eric Pincus of Bleacher Report about the Lakers’ impressive Game 2 win over the Blazers on Thursday night. The guys discuss the difficulty of playing in the bubble and the quarterback competition in New England!
